headline: CCL's Booking Visibility Strengthens: Can Demand Hold Amid Macro Noise?
summary: Carnival exits FY25 with record forward bookings, and two-thirds of 2026 sold at higher prices, signaling resilient cruise demand despite macro uncertainty.
